                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Word came down the path - the Takehara badge. The flock called it before the newspapers did."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The falls badge. My birds spotted you first, remember. I want that noted somewhere."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Ayo - after the badge",
                    Label: "badge_after"
                },
                {
                    Conditions: [
                        {
                            Type: "PLAYER_TAG",
                            Operation: "EQUALS",
                            Name: "defeated_sq_regular_spotter"
                        }
                    ],
                    Priority: 30,
                    Buttons: [
                        {
                            Name: "Goodbye",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "goodbye_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "You beat me fair. The road is yours to walk, today and always."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "My eyes only work once per trainer. Rules of the road. My brother Kwame up the road makes the same joke and tells it worse."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Ayo - beaten",
                    Label: "beaten"
                },
                {
                    Priority: 10,
