                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "You crossed my sightline. Rules of the road - eye contact means a battle. I did not invent the rules, I only enforce them from above."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "A bird keeper never blinks first. My flock saw you three bends back. Shall we?"
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "People tell me things about Leader Cicada. Blindfolds. Waterfalls. I have watched Cicada buy bread on a Tuesday like a regular person. A sightline beats a hundred rumors."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Ayo - spotted",
                    Label: "default"
                }
            ]
